---
// Standalone GPU Course page - no connection to main site
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>GPU Computing Crash Course</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #fafafa;
        --text: #1a1a1a;
        --text-muted: #666;
        --accent: #0ea5e9;
        --accent-dim: #0284c7;
        --border: #e5e5e5;
        --card-bg: #fff;
        --code-bg: #f4f4f5;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Source Sans 3', system-ui, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      }

      /* Header */
      header {
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      h1 {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      h1::before {
        content: '>';
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .subtitle {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      /* Sections */
      section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--text);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      h2::before {
        content: '#';
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      /* Resource Lists */
      .resources {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.75rem;
      }

      .resource {
        display: block;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
      }

      .resource:hover {
        border-color: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
      }

      .resource-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .resource-desc {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .resource-tag {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
        background: var(--code-bg);
        border-radius: 4px;
        color: var(--accent-dim);
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
      }

      /* Simple list variant */
      .link-list {
        list-style: none;
      }

      .link-list li {
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .link-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .link-list a {
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .link-list a:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .link-list a::after {
        content: 'â†’';
        color: var(--accent);
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.15s;
      }

      .link-list a:hover::after {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      /* Footer */
      footer {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>GPU Computing Crash Course</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          A curated collection of resources for learning CUDA and GPU programming.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section>
        <h2>Fundamentals</h2>
        <div class="resources">
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">CUDA C++ Programming Guide</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Official NVIDIA documentation covering the CUDA programming model.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">docs</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">GPU Architecture Overview</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Understanding SMs, warps, and the memory hierarchy.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">article</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Getting Started</h2>
        <div class="resources">
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">CUDA Toolkit Installation</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Setting up your development environment.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">setup</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">Your First CUDA Program</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Hello world and vector addition.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">tutorial</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Courses & Tutorials</h2>
        <div class="resources">
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">GPU Puzzles</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Sasha Rush's interactive GPU programming puzzles.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">interactive</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">PMPP Book</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Programming Massively Parallel Processors - the classic textbook.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">book</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Tools & Libraries</h2>
        <ul class="link-list">
          <li><a href="#">cuBLAS - GPU-accelerated BLAS</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">cuDNN - Deep learning primitives</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Triton - Python-like GPU programming</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Nsight - Profiling and debugging</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Practice</h2>
        <div class="resources">
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">CUDA Samples</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Official NVIDIA code samples.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">code</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="resource">
            <div class="resource-title">Project Ideas</div>
            <div class="resource-desc">Matrix multiplication, convolutions, parallel reductions.</div>
            <span class="resource-tag">exercises</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Advanced Topics</h2>
        <ul class="link-list">
          <li><a href="#">Memory coalescing and bank conflicts</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Occupancy optimization</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Tensor cores and mixed precision</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Multi-GPU programming</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p>Last updated: January 2026</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
